<br>
Giving an exsasperated sigh, she let go of the man, to fall where he stood, and turned on her heel and walked out the main door.<br>
<br>
The halfelf was planning to ask the other guard what was going on, but she stopped short, seeing the shape at teh gate, huge, to her halfelven frame.<br>
<br>
She made an agitated face to herself, took a breath and walked up to the Iksar.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
What is it YOU want? <p><center><a href="http://pub15.ezboard.com/bsarscorner" target="_new"><b>Sarhea Tu'Rilthiir</b></a><br>
